Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This superb office/warehouse facility is located within the Canningvale precinct not far from Bannister Road.Office area approx 226 sqm and a high truss ( 8 metres) warehouse of approx 898 sqm.Total net lettable area approx 1,124 sqm.

Dual front access into the warehouse with a loading dock.

There is potenatial to increase the building by approx 700 sqm or use the rear land as hardstand.

Excellent on-site parking as avaiable.

CBRE are pleased to offer for lease two modern buildings located at 21 Bannister Road Canning Vale.

Front building :

Office - 232 sqm

Factory/warehouse - 1,722 sqm.

The factory has an attached spray shed and a two (2) tonne gantry crane.Excellent on-site parking and exposure to Bannister Road.

------- ------------------------------ ------------------------------ ------------------------------

Rear building :

Office - 529 sqm

Factory/warehouse - 2,412 sqm
Mezzanine - 140 sqm.

The factory has three (3) x 5 tonne overhead cranes & spray booth with a 8 - 9 metre truss height..
There is ample parking and laydown areas.

These buildings can be leased together or separately.


These two buildings are being offer for lease at 50% of the current net rental being paid by the existing tenant.

For further details please contact either Geoff Fraser on 0413 624 000 or Warick Irving on 0413 863 335
